Macintosh,@{ub} with this installer, onto another disk/volume then copy those two components to your
original System folder, replacing the old/damaged ones.
  Here are my guide for using this alternative installer:

1) @{" Pic " LINK "MacGuideIV_Pics/MT4_Alt8Install1/main"} This is the alternative installer's @{b}Splash @{ub}screen.
2) @{" Pic " LINK "MacGuideIV_Pics/MT4_Alt8Install2/main"} Next you'll see the @{b}License Agreement @{ub}window. I suggest you give it a good read, there
