menu under "Preferences" in System 8 to 8.1. @{" Pic " LINK "MacGuideIV_Pics/MT3_CPsViews+Labels/main"}

@{B}WindowShade @{UB}
Specifies whether to hide a window by clicking on its title bar. Note: Can be found in the Edit
menu under "Preferences" in System 8 to 8.1. @{" Pic " LINK "MacGuideIV_Pics/MT3_CPsAuto&Menus/main"}
